# New Feature Template

When creating a new feature, mirror the structure in `lib/features/zfeature_template/`. Replace `zfeature` / `Zfeature` with the actual feature name throughout.

## Folder Structure

```
lib/features/<feature_name>/
  <feature_name>.dart          # barrel: exports view/ and bloc/
  bloc/
    bloc.dart                  # barrel: exports <feature_name>_bloc.dart
    <feature_name>_bloc.dart   # BLoC class + part directives
    <feature_name>_event.dart  # Freezed events (part of bloc)
    <feature_name>_state.dart  # Freezed states (part of bloc)
    <feature_name>_bloc.freezed.dart  # generated — do not edit
  view/
    view.dart                  # barrel: exports <feature_name>_page.dart
    <feature_name>_page.dart   # main page widget
```

## File Templates

### `<feature_name>.dart`
```dart
export 'view/view.dart';
export 'bloc/bloc.dart';
```

### `bloc/bloc.dart`
```dart
export '<feature_name>_bloc.dart';
```

### `bloc/<feature_name>_bloc.dart`
```dart
import 'package:bloc/bloc.dart';
import 'package:freezed_annotation/freezed_annotation.dart';

part '<feature_name>_event.dart';
part '<feature_name>_state.dart';
part '<feature_name>_bloc.freezed.dart';

class <FeatureName>Bloc extends Bloc<<FeatureName>Event, <FeatureName>State> {
  <FeatureName>Bloc() : super(const <FeatureName>State.initial()) {
    on<<FeatureName>Event>((event, emit) {
      // TODO: implement event handler
    });
  }
}
```

### `bloc/<feature_name>_event.dart`
```dart
part of '<feature_name>_bloc.dart';

@freezed
class <FeatureName>Event with _$<FeatureName>Event {
  const factory <FeatureName>Event.started() = _Started;
}
```

### `bloc/<feature_name>_state.dart`
```dart
part of '<feature_name>_bloc.dart';

@freezed
class <FeatureName>State with _$<FeatureName>State {
  const factory <FeatureName>State.initial() = _Initial;
}
```

### `view/view.dart`
```dart
export '<feature_name>_page.dart';
```

## After creating files
- Run `dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs` to generate the `.freezed.dart` file.
- Register the route in `lib/core/routes/app_pages.dart` and `app_routes.dart`.
